1 0 'MULTIPLE SOURCES' COMPLEX 'Human telomerase H/ACA RNP lobe' 
;The hTR H/ACA motif, which adopts a double-hairpin structure hinged by the H-box and flanked by the ACA box, scaffolds the assembly of two copies each of dyskerin, NHP2, NOP10 and GAR1, one on each hairpin. TCAB1 binds the CAB box.
